# Session [6] – Network+

## Main Topics
- Router chist? (what is router?)  
- Router chetor kar mikonad? (how does router work?)  
- Fargh router ba switch chist? (what is the difference between router and switch?)  

## Flashback – Router Basics
- Router = device ke chand network ra be ham vasl mikonad  
- Router **data ra be network mored nazar miresand**, na faghat be port  
- Router smart device ast, routing table va IP address ha ra mifahmad  
- Router ha ba estefade az information ke darn morevajeh change hashon mishan 

## Explanation
- Router = hardware baraye network  
- IP address ha ra check mikonad va packet ra be network mored nazar ersal mikonad  
- Fargh switch:  
  - Switch faghat LAN ro vasl mikonad va data ra be PC motelegh be MAC address miresand  
  - Router LAN ha ya network ha ra be ham vasl mikonad va IP layer ro handle mikonad  
- Estefade dar LAN ta WAN, baraye ersal internet va network haye bozorg  

